A sample project written in Mojolicious (not Lite).
See koorchik's blog  http://koorchik.blogspot.com/2010/11/mojolicious-lite.html (in Russian)

INSTALLATION
1. git clone git://github.com/koorchik/FastNotes-Proto.git fastnotes
2. cd fastnotes
3. install Carton and run "carton install". Or you can manually install all dependencies listed in Makefile.pl
4. perl script/fastnotes.pl daemon
